CREATE TABLE "t_equip" (
"equip_id"  INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
"e_color"  INTEGER,
"e_name"  TEXT,
"e_sex"  INTEGER,
"e_type"  INTEGER,
"e_attack"  INTEGER,
"e_speed"  INTEGER,
"e_defense"  INTEGER,
"e_level"  INTEGER,
"e_properties"  TEXT,
"e_job"  INTEGER,
"e_app"  TEXT,
"e_app_r"  TEXT,
"e_app_p"  TEXT,
"e_desc"  TEXT,
"e_tgl"  TEXT,
"e_pkg"  TEXT,
"crawl"  TEXT,
"jump"  TEXT,
"ladder"  TEXT,
"magic"  TEXT,
"magic_1"  TEXT,
"magic_2"  TEXT,
"onehand_1"  TEXT,
"onehand_2"  TEXT,
"onehand_3"  TEXT,
"rope"  TEXT,
"run_1"  TEXT,
"run_2"  TEXT,
"run_3"  TEXT,
"sit"  TEXT,
"stand_1"  TEXT,
"stand_2"  TEXT,
"stand_3"  TEXT,
"twohands_1"  TEXT,
"twohands_2"  TEXT,
"twohands_3"  TEXT,
"twohands_4"  TEXT,
"e_get"  INTEGER,
CONSTRAINT "color_equip" FOREIGN KEY ("e_color") REFERENCES "t_color" ("color_id"),
CONSTRAINT "type_equip" FOREIGN KEY ("e_type") REFERENCES "t_equip_type" ("type_id")
);
